(Evil company!)

00:05:54.900 --> 00:05:56.380
- Give us back our homes!
- Give us back our homes!

00:05:56.380 --> 00:05:58.580
(We'll keep following up on this story.)

00:06:01.790 --> 00:06:02.590
Mr. Lu.

00:06:04.150 --> 00:06:05.270
