00:06:51.200 --> 00:06:52.120
Understood.

00:07:04.230 --> 00:07:07.270
Don't worry, Mr. Lu.

00:07:07.560 --> 00:07:08.760
We'll handle it.

00:07:10.590 --> 00:07:12.640
If this isn't dealt with properly,

00:07:12.640 --> 00:07:14.270
